title: Golff Promotional Products Design Competition（Golff创意周边征集大赛作品）
body:
Golff Promotional Products Design Competition. Below are the entries of this competition. As some entries do not meet the basic rules, they will not be included in voting.
Golff创意周边征集大赛，下面是本次大赛的参赛作品，由于部分参赛作品不符合周边设计的基本要求，故不参与本次投票。

Prize：
The I Prize: Choose three promotional products
The II Prize: Choose two promotional products
The III Prize: Choose one promotional product
Participation Prize: Divided 80 GOF
奖项设置：
一等奖1名：任选三件周边产品
二等奖1名：任选两件周边产品
三等奖1名：任选一件周边产品
参与奖：瓜分80GOF

Voting time（投票时间）：2020/11/26 00:00 -2020/11/27 16:00
